items.title: Naked mole rats' DNA could hold key to long life
items.description: The bald, subterranean rats are the world's longest-lived rodent.

items.title: South African farm worker describes how women fed to pigs to 'dispose of evidence'

items.title: 'Joy and pain': Palestinians celebrate deal but fear confronting grief

items.title: Police fire rubber bullets as Madagascar protesters reject president's promises
